title: Episode #58 - Mark Goldenberg, LeeAnn, & ME
description: Composer, producer, & guitarist Mark Goldenberg sits down in the Mancave with ME and LeeAnn and talks about working with Bonnie Raitt, Linda Ronstadt, Natalie Imbruglia, Chris Issak, Waylon Jennings, Willie Nelson, Peter Frampton, Hugh Laurie, Jackson Browne and even William Shatner!
